 his house. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 895, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 882 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13527,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/11\/virtue-fajr-jamaah-jumuah\/","url_meta":{"origin":577,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Fajr: Dawn prayer in congregation on Friday","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 11, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the best of prayers to Allah is the dawn prayer in congregation on Friday.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 2790 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28121,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/ten-rakaat-sunan\/","url_meta":{"origin":577,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Voluntary Sunan prayers throughout day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: I prayed with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, two prostrations before and after noon prayer, two prostrations after sunset prayer, two prostrations after evening prayer, and two prostrations after Friday prayer. As for sunset and evening prayer, they were in his house. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41148,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/07\/special-hour-friday\/","url_meta":{"origin":577,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jumu&#8217;ah: Special hour of prayer on Friday","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 7, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn 'Abdillah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe day of Friday is made of twelve hours. No Muslim finds himself supplicating to Allah Almighty during one of them but that Allah will give it to him. Thus, seek it out in the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17474,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/05\/friday-jumuah-prayer-seal-heart\/","url_meta":{"origin":577,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Friday: Allah seals hearts of those who neglect Friday prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 5, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever hears the announcement of Friday prayer and he does not come, then he hears it again and does not come, then he hears it again and does not come, Allah will place a seal\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12964,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/18\/four-sunan-rakaat-after-jumuah\/","url_meta":{"origin":577,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Jumuah: Four Sunan cycles after Friday prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"When one of you performs Friday prayer, let him pray four cycles\u00a0after it.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 881 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"htt